{"tid":1776621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解12月10世界人權日乜行動都冇？","createTime":"2019-12-09T16:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T17:37:01.000Z","uid":201027,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e98cd4bd6e926bdd457dde05678ea46a6328e0ff","tid":1776621,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"今日先係正日喎，冇行動嘅？<br />\n贏咗啦？"},{"pid":"fca3d2d3661df6510578d25acc369235649008f6","tid":1776621,"uid":213163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"*已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n【國際人權日．正日集會】<br />\n<br />\n1948年12月10日，聯合國公佈《世界人權宣言》，確立生而為人的基本權利。走過71年，世界人權仍然是未竟之路。在香港及世界各地，人民仍要為爭取基本的自由及權利奮鬥，甚至有所付出及犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n12月10日晚，我們一起站出來，為香港人加油，也為全球為人權奮鬥的人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n日期：12月10日<br />\n時間：18:30-22:00<br />\n地點：金鐘連儂牆下<br />\n<br />\n內容：<br />\n悼念及回顧<br />\n嘉賓講話<br />\n短片欣賞及分享<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D6enJSs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD6enJSs.jpg&h=f8fc244f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推呀屌你再過20個鐘就係啦 唔好再屌鬼啦行動post呢文宣post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日要見到大家出嚟"},{"pid":"e19623748192c99089df48c6834b774ca1ba0c23","tid":1776621,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"你而家post我先見咋喎<br />\n一向都只見呢張<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkhgOkv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkhgOkv.png&h=91a68db2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba708c89bcf3e1282b896779266d4af0e73432e5","tid":1776621,"uid":213163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e19623748192c99089df48c6834b774ca1ba0c23","tid":1776621,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"你而家post我先見咋喎<br />\n一向都只見呢張<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkhgOkv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkhgOkv.png&h=91a68db